Intercom Admin Panel Clone
This project is a responsive, React-based clone of the Intercom admin panel, created as part of an assignment to replicate the UI and core functionalities showcased in the provided demo video.

🚀 Live Demo
http://192.168.186.148:3000/

📂 Features
Modern UI: Sidebar navigation, header, chat list, and chat window

Responsive Design: Works on desktop and mobile devices

Transitions & Animations: Smooth hover and selection effects

Dummy Data: All data is mocked for demonstration

Component-based Structure: Clean, modular React code

React

CSS (with custom component styles)

Vercel for deployment

📱 Mobile Responsiveness
The UI is fully responsive and adapts to various screen sizes, ensuring a seamless experience on both desktop and mobile.

🛠️ Getting Started
Clone the repo:

bash
git clone https://github.com/VB4819/intercom-clone.git
cd intercom-clone
Install dependencies:

bash
npm install
Run the app locally:

bash
npm start
The app will open at http://localhost:3000.

📝 Assignment Notes
Focus: UI/UX, responsiveness, and code quality

Functionality: Replicates the main layout and chat flow as seen in the demo video

Limitations: Uses only dummy data, no backend/API integration

Libraries Used: Only React and CSS

